OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud but a
OL,6,Fgenerally fine, bright and rather warm
OL,7,Fday. Cloud increasing by late
OL,8,Fafternoon, perhaps bringing some rain,
OL,9,Fmainly across western hills by early
OL,10,Fevening. Breezy at times, especially
OL,11,Fduring the afternoon with occasional
OL,12,Fgusty winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FTurning cloudy across all
OL,15,Fparts through the evening with
OL,16,Foutbreaks of mainly light rain
OL,17,Fspreading east overnight. More
OL,18,Fpersistent rain with heavier bursts
OL,19,Flikely in the far west after dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
